title: Nelly's Kitchen
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Organic, Western, Juice bar, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Israeli, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Health food restaurant in Jaffa's flea market. Uses mostly organic ingredients and whole food products, and has vegetarian and vegan choices. Offers breakfast all day, business lunch until 5pm, daily specials.
